Business Context
 
The Mat works operates in a council-owned repurposed historical prison site, mainly focusing on arts and music hosting concerts and events, whilst having other multi-purpose facilities such as rehearsal rooms, a café/bar, and a main auditorium. Everyone is able to use these facilities as The Mat Works serves both public visitors and professional musicians.
 
