The development workflow outlines the structured process that will be followed to design and build The Mat Works Venue Management and Booking System. Establishing a clear workflow ensures that the project is organised, efficient, and aligned with the client’s requirements at every stage. It also helps maintain consistency across the system’s components, from early planning through to final evaluation.
